    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The action or condition of causing something, such as a group of people or a settlement, to exist. Founding usually involves official documents and official naming, and occurs on a specific date. For reference to less formal beginnings of groups of people or other things, use "establishment (action or condition)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
